Colombia Bank Discussed Risks of Prolonged Period of Low Rates

-- B y   H e l e n   M u r p h y
-- 
2011-03-11T15:17:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/colombia-bank-discussed-risks-of-prolonged-period-of-low-rates.html
  Colombia ’s central bank policy
makers discussed the risk of prolonged periods of low  interest
rates  on financial stability, economic growth and inflation
before unexpectedly increasing the benchmark interest rate 25
basis points, according to minutes of the board’s Feb. 25
meeting published today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
